{"about_the_game":"<strong>Description</strong><br><i>&quot;The Baron's daughter is missing, and you are the man to find her. No problem. With your inexhaustible arsenal of hard-boiled similes, there is nothing you can't handle.&quot;</i><br><br>PataNoir is a homage to the classic stories of hard-boiled private investigators with a knack for describing everything with complex similes and metaphors. In PataNoir, you solve problems by manipulating the hard-boiled metaphors used by the main character to make sense of the world in which he lives.<br><br>The game is an old-school text adventure, in which you type commands to perform actions.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> An interactive noir mystery to experience and solve<br></li><li> Innovative interactive fiction gameplay in which the metaphors you live by become tools to solve the mystery<br></li><li> Simulated book interface<br></li><li> Atmospheric illustrations by Lauri Ahonen and Tom Siddell<br></li><li> Original theme song by postmodern rock musician William Steffey</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Detective","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/449150/b08658f4c3d7cdfd953652eae58fb1026c5fa294.jpg"},{"name":"Graduate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/449150/9b6e0b757fdc42da3e88a99c76a85ad43be7de26.jpg"},{"name":"Visitor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/449150/6e317e0f768e2dc5c71e190193ddb7cf50a1aa57.jpg"},{"name":"Snake handler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/449150/670a5c442c4c3161fbf184bc3ed052a695ee6c59.jpg"},{"name":"Intruder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/449150/e1792743c498cac33838d4989864d55840ec3e05.jpg"},{"name":"Gambler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/449150/9336047ef6fc2deb255a08819fc0046d071